member.name: T:Symbol.XamarinEMDK.EMDKManager
member.summary: The EMDKManager class is the key class in Android EMDK. This class provides access to different classes for the supported features. Clients should call EMDKManager.getEMDKManager(Context, EMDKManager.EMDKListener), to get the EMDKManager object. Each application implements EMDKListener interface. The EMDKManager object will be returned on successful opening through the EMDKListener callback.
